[
  {
    "startTime": 0.12,
    "endTime": 1.85,
    "text": "These are our cats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.85,
    "endTime": 3.8200000000000003,
    "text": "They're a bit unique."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.45,
    "endTime": 5.68,
    "text": "This is Haku."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.68,
    "endTime": 7.9,
    "text": "He's a big boye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.96,
    "endTime": 9.879999999999999,
    "text": "You're so big. You're so big."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.92,
    "endTime": 11.86,
    "text": "Haku likes watching things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.96,
    "endTime": 22.16,
    "text": "Which side do you want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.26,
    "endTime": 25.32,
    "text": "And he's obsessed with sticks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.18,
    "endTime": 28.56,
    "text": "ANY kind of stick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.12,
    "endTime": 33.059999999999995,
    "text": "That's mine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.08,
    "endTime": 33.96,
    "text": "Haku?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.38,
    "endTime": 35.400000000000006,
    "text": "Haku?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.62,
    "endTime": 37.98,
    "text": "I mean, I can drink without a straw but you know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.98,
    "endTime": 39.919999999999995,
    "text": "you don't have to ruin it just for fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.94,
    "endTime": 42.78,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.64,
    "endTime": 45.6,
    "text": "What? What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.18,
    "endTime": 57.36,
    "text": "Oh nonono"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.38,
    "endTime": 62.32,
    "text": "Can I eat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.4,
    "endTime": 66.36,
    "text": "Whenever we shower he has to rub his face\r\non our hair and try to eat it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.78,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "He likes to smoosh his face when he sleeps."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.48,
    "endTime": 81.54,
    "text": "And he's got a bit of a thing for armpits."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.56,
    "endTime": 82.52,
    "text": "Bud..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.14,
    "endTime": 87.42,
    "text": "This is Poki."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.42,
    "endTime": 90.18,
    "text": "We found him on the expressway and now he's\r\nobsessed with food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.18,
    "endTime": 91.66000000000001,
    "text": "You ready for food?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.5,
    "endTime": 104.02,
    "text": "Last time we checked in with Poki he kept\r\nclimbing into the trash can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.02,
    "endTime": 105.52,
    "text": "but now he's evolved."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.52,
    "endTime": 108.47999999999999,
    "text": "He knows that if he climbs into the trash\r\ncan he can't get out, so now he sits on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.5,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "so now he sits on the side and tries to pull\r\nthings out with his paws and mouth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.9,
    "endTime": 138.26000000000002,
    "text": "Please don't eat that, bud. Please don't eat that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.92,
    "endTime": 145.79999999999998,
    "text": "Poki, what are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.8,
    "endTime": 147.9,
    "text": "nothing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.9,
    "endTime": 151.24,
    "text": "I was just staring out this window"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.58,
    "endTime": 157.42000000000002,
    "text": "Don't act like you weren't doing anything!\r\nI just saw you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.44,
    "endTime": 159.06,
    "text": "He's also very licky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.92,
    "endTime": 166.98,
    "text": "He likes to cuddle and sleeps in between our\r\npillows every night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.0,
    "endTime": 170.12,
    "text": "This is Nagi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.12,
    "endTime": 172.04,
    "text": "He's a good boye who follows the rules."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.18,
    "endTime": 178.019,
    "text": "We adopted him when no one else would because\r\nhe needed a little tummy surgery."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.02,
    "endTime": 180.22,
    "text": "When he wants to play he trills to let me\r\nknow he's ready."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.08,
    "endTime": 212.96,
    "text": "Is this what you want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.6,
    "endTime": 216.0,
    "text": "This what you want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.54,
    "endTime": 226.0,
    "text": "He really, really likes plastic wrappers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.86,
    "endTime": 255.5,
    "text": "Bring the plastic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.46,
    "endTime": 264.14,
    "text": "What, you wanna play?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.64,
    "endTime": 269.28,
    "text": "He also gets really sad when he finds a bug\r\nbut can't reach it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.06,
    "endTime": 290.72,
    "text": "We have to be careful to vacuum a lot because\r\nif he finds fur on the floor he eats it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.72,
    "endTime": 292.8,
    "text": "Stop! Will you stop eating that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.54,
    "endTime": 296.97900000000004,
    "text": "He doesn't like being pet during the day\r\nbut sometimes in the early morning he comes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.98,
    "endTime": 299.66,
    "text": "to cuddle in bed with us and purrs himself\r\nto sleep for a little bit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.12,
    "endTime": 302.56,
    "text": "Cats vs playtime"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.02,
    "endTime": 308.0,
    "text": "Poki is a little over-enthusiastic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.64,
    "endTime": 315.0,
    "text": "Nagi plays to kill."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.22,
    "endTime": 333.851,
    "text": "Even though Haku is the biggest and strongest,\r\nhe's too scared to play with toys when the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.86,
    "endTime": 335.5,
    "text": "other two are out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.36,
    "endTime": 338.68,
    "text": "…which is understandable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.1,
    "endTime": 344.92,
    "text": "That is, unless I get out a stick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.22,
    "endTime": 350.76000000000005,
    "text": "Poki doesn't really care about the vacuum\r\ncleaner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.92,
    "endTime": 355.62,
    "text": "Nagi is extremely terrified."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.58,
    "endTime": 359.4,
    "text": "Haku… is pretty into it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.56,
    "endTime": 378.7,
    "text": "Cats vs box"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.82,
    "endTime": 380.54,
    "text": "Haku loves boxes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.64,
    "endTime": 395.38,
    "text": "Poki doesn't really care"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.2,
    "endTime": 404.64,
    "text": "Nagi is curious..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.08,
    "endTime": 407.53999999999996,
    "text": "but only a little."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 415.36,
    "endTime": 417.90000000000003,
    "text": "Let's see what happens if I turn the box sideways."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.06,
    "endTime": 421.76,
    "text": "Poki still doesn't really care."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 423.7,
    "endTime": 426.5,
    "text": "Haku still really loves boxes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.14,
    "endTime": 432.4,
    "text": "And Nagi is still curious..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.7,
    "endTime": 436.9,
    "text": "but only a little."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.06,
    "endTime": 444.0,
    "text": "I decided to see if Nagi would go in the box\r\nif Haku wasn't inside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.38,
    "endTime": 460.0,
    "text": "But he just wants to play."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.18,
    "endTime": 490.56,
    "text": "This just in!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490.56,
    "endTime": 495.59,
    "text": "Using public wifi, whether you're at a café,\r\na grocery store, or even a hotel, leaves you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.59,
    "endTime": 498.96,
    "text": "your passwords and other sensitive data at\r\nrisk of being hacked!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.96,
    "endTime": 503.48999999999995,
    "text": "Thanks to today's sponsor, NordVPN, you\r\ncan protect yourself online with military"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.49,
    "endTime": 505.009,
    "text": "grade encryption."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.009,
    "endTime": 508.5,
    "text": "Have you ever tried to watch a video and been\r\nblocked because it's not available in your region?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.02,
    "endTime": 510.02,
    "text": "I wouldn't know what that's like."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.42,
    "endTime": 511.28000000000003,
    "text": "I'm a cat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.289,
    "endTime": 516.97,
    "text": "But NordVPN has thousands of servers in 62\r\ncountries so you can watch content from anywhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516.97,
    "endTime": 520.979,
    "text": "One account can have up to 6 connections so\r\nall your phones and computers can be protected"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.979,
    "endTime": 522.07,
    "text": "at the same time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.07,
    "endTime": 527.85,
    "text": "Sign up at NordVPN.com/rachelandjun or use\r\nthe code rachelandjun to get 77% off a 3-year"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.85,
    "endTime": 528.85,
    "text": "plan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.85,
    "endTime": 532.85,
    "text": "That's only $2.75 a month, for the best\r\nVPN out there!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.85,
    "endTime": 535.7900000000001,
    "text": "And don't wait, this offer is ending soon."
  }
]